window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Realm of Dreich is a getaway for the rich and powerful, a medieval-inspired town in the middle of a vast frozen wilderness. Now itâ€™s the site of a wedding, intended to join two feuding families who have spent centuries in an uneasy truce with each other.</p> <p>When Tommy Carpenter asks his best friend, Nate Garrett, to help him with the security of the wedding, Nate reluctantly agrees, knowing that it will be a long weekend of work and, in all probability, treachery.</p> <p>It is only a matter of time before members of each family are found murdered and it is up to Nate and Tommy to find the killer before more bodies fall, potentially reigniting a war.</p>"; 
